<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/304406-did-anyone-else-feel-this-book-was-all">Did anyone else feel this book was all about nothing?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_304406'><a id="like_count_community_question_304406" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/304406?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">4 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F41951.Scarlet_Feather">like</a></span>

