<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1360572-is-this-the-only-book-featuring-these">Is this the only book featuring these caterers?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1360572'><a id="like_count_community_question_1360572" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1360572?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F41951.Scarlet_Feather">like</a></span>

